de the characters in string literals - they will be automatically encoded via JSON escape sequences (\\uXXXX) during transmission and properly decoded in IDA"}, "ida_target": {"type": "string", "description": "Optional IDA target alias. Configure via IDA_TARGETS (example: A=127.0.0.1:31337;B=127.0.0.1:31338)."}}, "required": ["code"]}}]}}
